<section class="section aerys-problem" id="problem" aria-labelledby="problem-title">
  <div class="container">

    <span class="sec-label">The Root Cause</span>
    <h2 id="problem-title" class="aerys-problem__headline">
      Your body is running on a <span class="hi">30% oxygen deficit</span><br>every single night.
    </h2>

    <!-- Scannable symptoms — instantly relatable -->
    <div class="aerys-problem__symptoms" role="list" aria-label="Common symptoms">
      <div class="aerys-problem__symptom" role="listitem">
        <div class="aerys-problem__symptom-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M17 14V2"/><path d="M9 18.12 10 14H4.17a2 2 0 0 1-1.92-2.56l2.33-8A2 2 0 0 1 6.5 2H20a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v8a2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-2.76a2 2 0 0 0-1.79 1.11L12 22h0a3.13 3.13 0 0 1-3-3.88Z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span>Wake up exhausted after 8 hours</span>
      </div>
      <div class="aerys-problem__symptom" role="listitem">
        <div class="aerys-problem__symptom-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M12 16v-4M12 8h.01"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span>Brain fog and low energy by mid-morning</span>
      </div>
      <div class="aerys-problem__symptom" role="listitem">
        <div class="aerys-problem__symptom-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span>Dry, paste-dry mouth every morning</span>
      </div>
      <div class="aerys-problem__symptom" role="listitem">
        <div class="aerys-problem__symptom-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <span>Partner complains about your snoring</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="aerys-problem__body">
      <p>This isn&rsquo;t a discipline problem. This isn&rsquo;t a mattress problem. This isn&rsquo;t even a stress problem &mdash; though the stress is real.</p>
      <p class="aerys-problem__emphasis">It&rsquo;s a breathing problem.</p>
      <p>When your mouth falls open during sleep, your body switches from nasal breathing &mdash; which filters, warms, and efficiently processes oxygen &mdash; to oral breathing, which does none of those things. Your O&#8322; exchange efficiency drops by up to 30%. Your nervous system registers a threat, elevates cortisol, and fragments your sleep cycles. You never reach the deep REM your brain and body depend on to restore themselves.</p>
      <p>You spend 7, 8, even 9 hours in bed. And you wake up exhausted because your body spent the night in low-grade physiological crisis.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Lifestyle image -->
    <div class="aerys-problem__visual">
      <img
        src="https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0808/8112/3545/files/product-woman.png?v=1776730990"
        alt="Woman sleeping comfortably with AERYS™ mouth tape applied"
        class="aerys-problem__img"
        width="1100"
        height="520"
        loading="lazy"
      >
    </div>

    <p class="aerys-problem__cards-label">Three things happen to your body every night you mouth breathe:</p>

    <div class="aerys-problem__cards">

      <div class="aerys-problem__card">
        <div class="aerys-problem__card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="aerys-problem__card-title">Chronic Fatigue</h3>
        <p class="aerys-problem__card-desc">Reduced oxygen exchange disrupts cellular energy production. You wake up in oxygen debt before the day even starts.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aerys-problem__card">
        <div class="aerys-problem__card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M2 12s3-7 10-7 10 7 10 7-3 7-10 7-10-7-10-7z"/><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="aerys-problem__card-title">Fragmented Sleep</h3>
        <p class="aerys-problem__card-desc">Oral airway collapse triggers micro-arousals throughout the night &mdash; pulling you out of deep sleep so consistently your REM architecture never forms properly.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="aerys-problem__card">
        <div class="aerys-problem__card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M20.84 4.61a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 0L12 5.67l-1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 00-7.78 7.78l1.06 1.06L12 21.23l7.78-7.78 1.06-1.06a5.5 5.5 0 000-7.78z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="aerys-problem__card-title">Cumulative Structural Damage</h3>
        <p class="aerys-problem__card-desc">Years of open-mouth sleep alter mandibular position, facial muscle tone, and jaw alignment. The changes are slow. They are not reversible on their own.</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

